name: Corn Walk
description:
This is a personal project. You found yourself in the middle of an endless corn field. 

Download it. Play it for 1 or 2 minutes. Get lost in yourself as the tall plants appear endlessly in front of you. Wander. Then get back to whatever you were doing.

It is written in python3 using the pyglet module, and then converted to exe with pyinstaller. You might have some trouble with your antivirus, sorry about that.
